OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with some bright spells to
OL,6,Fstart. Cloud thickening from late
OL,7,Fmorning with rain then spreading
OL,8,Fnortheastwards through the afternoon
OL,9,Fand becoming heavy at times. Light
OL,10,Fwinds becoming strong southeasterlies
OL,11,Fwith risk of coastal gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy rain clearing to the
OL,14,Feast through the evening to leave the
OL,15,Frest of the night dry with some clear
OL,16,Fspells developing. Strong winds and
OL,17,Frisk of coastal gales easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
