OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Becoming cloudier in the
OL,7,Fafternoon with outbreaks of rain which
OL,8,Fmay be heavy at times. Winds strong at
OL,9,Ftimes, especially near the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday. Sunny
OL,13,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,15,FTuesday. Winds will be strong with
OL,16,Frisk of gales Sunday, then becoming
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
